          "rotation": 0.0,
          "has_text": true,
          "text": "9 March 2026: MoH Data Platform Project introduction (previous meeting)\r16 March 2026: Initial Data Platform project briefing held with NSW Health project team\r16 March 2026: Data matching clarification provided to eHealth\r25 March 2026: Data Platform project timeline shared with NSW Health project team\r2 April 2026: Technical discussion held with DAC and NSW Health on the Data Platform project, with a preliminary decision to ingest data from ADLS into Snowflake to reuse existing engineering and simplify NSW Health integration\r13 April 2026: Confirmation provided to NSW Health on data transfer encryption and endpoint setup\r16 April 2026: MoH Data Platform Project update (this meeting)",
