          "height": 291.968505859375,
          "rotation": 0.0,
          "has_text": true,
          "text": "March 2026\rFinalise foundational design and onboarding activities.\rConfirm scope, sequencing and readiness for the main build phase.\rProject tracking indicates this phase is on track and approaching a critical transition point.\rApril 2026\rComplete remaining foundation work and close out early-stage dependencies.\rRamp up core build activities for delivery across the remainder of the year.\rFinal opportunity to stabilise the overall approach before downstream activities accelerate.\rMay 2026\rEnter full report build phase for datasets.\rData ingestion, transformation and platform components progress in parallel.\rDependencies between workstreams become active and closely coordinated.\r",
          "fill_rgb": null,
          "line_rgb": null,
          "font_name": "Aptos",
          "font_size": 18.0,
          "font_bold": -2,
