          "height": 291.968505859375,
          "rotation": 0.0,
          "has_text": true,
          "text": "June 2026\rContinue core build with increasing integration between components.\rEarly outputs emerge, supporting progressive validation.\rJuly 2026 to February 2027 (expected project completion)\rTransition from core build into stabilisation and rollout, with expanding platform capability across data domains and increasing focus on controls, validation and reliable end to end operation.\rThrough August and September, data flows are strengthened and the platform progresses toward operational readiness.\rBy October and November, implementation winds down and attention shifts to consolidation, optimisation and structured handover.\rCore delivery is completed in December 2026, with the platform confirmed to be operating as intended.\rJanuary 2027 focuses on training, documentation and transition to business-as-usual operations, leading to formal project closure in February 2027 with the NSW Health data platform fully established and embedded.\r",
          "fill_rgb": null,
